name: Starbucks
description: If anti-worker practices and poor treatment is your jam, be ready to pour your savings into stupidly intricate caffeinated drinks.
review: I have literally never ordered anything from here in my entire life but the white woman collective of my family enjoys their venti vanilla bean frappuchinos with two pumps of cinnamon dolce syrup and two pumps of white mocha topped with caramel drizzle and cinnamon dolce sprinkles quite a bit.

name: Dunkin'
description: America runs, walks, works, and sleeps on Dunkin's coffee and donuts... as long as they aren't going to Starbucks or Sheetz.
review: Many great stories down in the reviews. Tanner loves the food but agrees it's "very not welcoming lmao", Owen and Brian can't agree on if they like the foreign and middle eastern workers or not, Carol got 3 drinks spilled everywhere, and Bill got cussed out for no reason but recommends doughnuts.
